][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-center donation-other\"]\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Difusión de Cáritas en redes sociales</h4>\r\nUna forma muy fácil de ayudar, es difundir la obra de Cáritas en redes sociales, síguenos y comparte nuestro contenido. Dejar la indiferencia es el primer paso para ayudar a los más necesitados. ¡Cáritas somos todos!\r\n[easy-followers title=\"\" new_window=\"1\" nofollow=\"1\" template=\"roundcolor\" columns=\"4\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"mt-4 pt-3 mb-3\"][vc_column][conecta items=\"6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" full_height=\"yes\"][vc_column][vc_wp_text]\r\n<div id=\"donation-form-b8ac1d50e32e7ec2b205\" role=\"main\"></div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://d335luupugsy2.cloudfront.net/js/rdstation-forms/stable/rdstation-forms.min.js\"></script> <script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n  new RDStationForms(\'donation-form-b8ac1d50e32e7ec2b205-html\', \'UA-111460820-1\').createForm();\r\n</script>[/vc_wp_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Inicio','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2018-09-20 06:47:39','2018-09-20 06:47:39','',2,'https://www.caritas.org.mx/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(780,1,'2018-09-20 07:26:04','2018-09-20 07:26:04','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_basic_grid post_type=\"post\" max_items=\"100\" grid_id=\"vc_gid:1537428158935-2106f785-688f-7\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','test-donation-form','','inherit','closed','closed','','752-revision-v1','','','2018-09-20 07:26:04','2018-09-20 07:26:04','',752,'https://www.caritas.org.mx/752-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(779,1,'2018-09-20 07:22:37','2018-09-20 07:22:37','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_basic_grid post_type=\"post\" max_items=\"100\" style=\"pagination\" items_per_page=\"5\" grid_id=\"vc_gid:1537428111357-6cfa35d9-a917-6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','test-donation-form','','inherit','closed','closed','','752-revision